Name: assign_team_to_project
Description: Whether a team is assigned to a project

Name: assign_worker_to_team
Description: Whether a worker belongs to a team

Name: assign_worker_role
Description: Whether a worker takes on a specific role

Name: assign_worker_skill
Description: Whether a worker is mapped to a skill

Name: select_feature_for_release
Description: Whether a feature is included in a release plan

Name: place_story_in_sprint
Description: Whether a user story is assigned to a sprint backlog

Name: select_task_for_sprint
Description: Whether a task is included on the sprint board

Name: close_blocker
Description: Whether a blocker is resolved in the sprint

Name: set_sprint_goal_achieved
Description: Flag for sprint goal achievement status

Name: allocate_budget_to_feature
Description: Continuous share of project budget allocated to a feature

Name: assign_product_owner_to_backlog
Description: Whether a product owner manages a backlog

Name: assign_scrum_master_to_team
Description: Whether a scrum master supports a team
